<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 18:15:07 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>消息人士称，阿美公司即将同意持有雷诺、吉利热力发动机合资公司10%的股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/aramco-close-agreeing-10-stake-renault-geely-thermal-engines-jv-sources-say-2024-06-27/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，沙特阿美公司将持有雷诺和中国吉利之间一家名为 Horse Powertrain 的热力发动机合资企业 10% 的股份，在电动汽车销售放缓之际，该公司将加强向传统汽车制造商供货的业务。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 18:02:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/aramco-close-agreeing-10-stake-renault-geely-thermal-engines-jv-sources-say-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>维吾尔组织赢得了英国对“奴工”棉花调查的上诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uyghur-group-wins-appeal-over-uk-probe-into-slave-labour-cotton-2024-06-27/</link><description>伦敦一家法院周四裁定，英国当局必须重新考虑是否对据称由中国新疆地区奴隶劳动生产的棉花进口展开调查，并允许维吾尔人权组织提出上诉。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:54:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uyghur-group-wins-appeal-over-uk-probe-into-slave-labour-cotton-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>墨西哥将寻求与中国锂公司就有争议的采矿特许权达成协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/mexico-seek-deal-over-disputed-mining-concession-with-chinese-lithium-firm-2024-06-27/</link><description>墨西哥总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔周四表示，在中国锂矿企业赣锋锂业就有争议的特许权提起仲裁后，墨西哥政府将寻求与该公司达成协议，同时仍捍卫墨西哥的权利。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:53:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/mexico-seek-deal-over-disputed-mining-concession-with-chinese-lithium-firm-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国针对欧盟猪肉的潜在行动对巴西来说可能是双刃剑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/potential-china-action-against-eu-pork-may-be-double-edged-sword-brazil-2024-06-27/</link><description>分析师和行业消息人士称，中国可能对欧盟猪肉进口实施反倾销措施，这对欧盟来说是一场灾难，可能有利于巴西出口商，但也会影响该国在其他地方的竞争能力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:32:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/potential-china-action-against-eu-pork-may-be-double-edged-sword-brazil-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>前货币政策委员会委员称英国央行可能在八月降息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bank-england-likely-cut-rates-august-former-mpc-member-says-2024-06-27/</link><description>一位前货币政策委员会成员周四表示，只要通胀和工资数据符合货币政策委员会 (MPC) 5 月份的预测，英国央行可能很快就会降息，“可能是在 8 月份”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 13:56:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bank-england-likely-cut-rates-august-former-mpc-member-says-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>在中国在南海的行动中，美国重申对菲律宾的“铁杆”承诺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-reiterates-ironclad-commitment-philippines-amid-china-actions-south-china-sea-2024-06-27/</link><description>白宫周四在两国国家安全顾问会谈后表示，在中国在南海的行动中，美国重申了对菲律宾安全的承诺。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 13:36:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-reiterates-ironclad-commitment-philippines-amid-china-actions-south-china-sea-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国共产党开除两名前国防部长因腐败</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-expels-two-former-defence-ministers-corruption-2024-06-27/</link><description>据官方通讯社新华社报道，中国共产党周四以“严重违纪”为由开除前国防部长李尚福及其前任魏凤和，这是对腐败的委婉说法。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 11:46:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-expels-two-former-defence-ministers-corruption-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国芯片制造商 Nexperia 投资 2 亿美元拓展欧洲业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-owned-chipmaker-nexperia-invests-200-mln-european-expansion-2024-06-27/</link><description>全球最大的二极管和晶体管等基础半导体制造商之一安世半导体周四表示，将投资 2 亿美元扩大其位于德国汉堡的主要生产基地的产能。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 08:11:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-owned-chipmaker-nexperia-invests-200-mln-european-expansion-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>台湾警告不要在处决威胁后前往中国大陆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-tells-its-citizens-avoid-unnecessary-travel-china-2024-06-27/</link><description>继北京上周威胁处决那些被视为“顽固”台独支持者之后，台湾政府周四提高了对中国大陆的旅行警告，告诉其公民除非绝对必要，否则不要前往。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 08:09:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-tells-its-citizens-avoid-unnecessary-travel-china-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国希望与欧盟达成适合双方的电动汽车关税协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-hopes-reach-mutually-acceptable-solutions-with-eu-ev-tariffs-2024-06-27/</link><description>中国商务部周四表示，中国希望与欧盟就定于 7 月 4 日生效的中国电动汽车初步关税谈判达成“双方都能接受的解决方案”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 07:32:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-hopes-reach-mutually-acceptable-solutions-with-eu-ev-tariffs-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>尽管央行警告风险，但中国资金仍流入债券</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-money-flows-into-bonds-even-central-bank-warns-risks-2024-06-27/</link><description>中国国债期货周四跃升至新高，而长期收益率则触及历史低点，因为投资者无视央行一再发出的风险警告，继续将资金投入债券。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 07:22:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-money-flows-into-bonds-even-central-bank-warns-risks-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>焦点：随着中国主导俄罗斯电动汽车市场，Zeekr 销量猛增</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/zeekrs-sales-jump-chinese-dominate-russian-ev-market-2024-06-27/</link><description>去年，Zeekr 电动汽车在俄罗斯的销量猛增，使中国汽车制造商在俄罗斯规模虽小但发展迅速的电动汽车 (EV) 行业中处于领先地位。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 07:03:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/zeekrs-sales-jump-chinese-dominate-russian-ev-market-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称，中国共产党将于 7 月 15 日至 18 日举行重要的三中全会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-hold-key-third-plenum-july-15-18-state-media-say-2024-06-27/</link><description>据新华社周四报道，中国共产党将于 7 月 15 日至 18 日举行拖延已久的三中全会。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 05:45:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-hold-key-third-plenum-july-15-18-state-media-say-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国将对进口欧盟甲苯胺启动反倾销复审</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-start-review-anti-dumping-measures-imports-eus-toluidine-2024-06-27/</link><description>中国商务部周四表示，中国将对进口欧盟甲苯胺（用于染料、药品和农药）启动反倾销期终复审。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 01:31:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-start-review-anti-dumping-measures-imports-eus-toluidine-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国为应对致命洪水的城市提供超过3.16亿美元的紧急救援</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-provides-additional-natural-disaster-relief-funds-says-state-media-2024-06-27/</link><description>由于近两周的暴雨肆虐中国多个地区，造成致命的洪水和山体滑坡，中国提供了超过23亿元人民币（3.164亿美元）的资金，以帮助救援工作、应急物资和规划。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 00:53:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-provides-additional-natural-disaster-relief-funds-says-state-media-2024-06-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>